column6: Deadpool is trying to stay one step ahead of Outlaw as he searches for a mysterious scientist in the jungle. In Washington, DC. a power struggle is under way at the highest levels of government that will turn Deadpool's world upside down.
column8: | writer:Mike Benson | writer:Adam Glass | penciller:Laurence Campbell | letterer:Chris Eliopoulos | colorist:Lee Loughridge
